OL,6,FCharlotte Dujardin's mentor and GB
OL,7,Fteammate Carl Hester has "universally
OL,8,Fcondemned" her actions after a video
OL,9,Fshowed the dressage rider repeatedly
OL,10,Fwhipping a horse during a training
OL,11,Fsession.
OL,13,FDujardin started her career in the
OL,14,Fsport under the tutelage of Hester and
OL,15,Fthe pair won team and individual gold
OL,16,Fat the London 2012 Olympics.
