OL,6,FThe footage from four years ago and
OL,7,Freleased by an anonymous whistleblower
OL,8,Fportrays Dujardin, a triple Olympic
OL,9,Fgold medalist, using a long whip to
OL,10,Fhit the legs of a horse more than 20
OL,11,Ftimes.
OL,13,FShe has since withdrawn from the Paris
OL,14,FOlympics and has been provisionally
OL,15,Fsuspended by The International
OL,16,FFederation for Equestrian Sports (FEI).
OL,18,FDujardin says she is "deeply ashamed"
OL,19,Fof her actions while Hester, who will
OL,20,Fcompete for Team GB next week at his
OL,21,Fseventh Games, signed a letter from
