OL,6,Fthe International Dressage Riders Club
OL,7,F(IDRC) to denounce what happened.
OL,9,FIt includes the following: "The IDRC
OL,10,Funiversally condemn the actions of
OL,11,FCharlotte Dujardin as seen in the
OL,12,Fvideo footage.
OL,14,F"The Board members are resolute that
OL,15,Fequine welfare must always be placed
OL,16,Fuppermost and at all times.
