OL,3,CCharlotte Dujardin's mentor
OL,4,C'universally condemns' her actions
OL,6,F"The IDRC Board supports the actions
OL,7,Ftaken by the FEI, the British
OL,8,FEquestrian Federation and British
OL,9,FDressage to provisionally suspend Ms
OL,10,FDujardin."
OL,12,FHester grew up on the small Channel
OL,13,FIsland of Sark and is one of the
OL,14,Flongest-serving British Olympians in
OL,15,Fhistory.
OL,17,FHe is part of the quartet of Team GB
OL,18,Friders taking part in dressage
OL,19,Fcompetitions at the Games this summer
OL,20,Fwith Becky Moody replacing Dujardin.
